## UI/UX Design Guidelines

### Design Philosophy
- **Minimalist & Clean**: Follow Apple and GitHub design principles
- **Light Theme Only**: Use light backgrounds with dark text (no dark theme)
- **Professional & Modern**: Corporate-friendly, suitable for enterprise applications
- **Content-First**: Remove unnecessary decorations, focus on functionality

### Color Palette
**Primary Colors:**
- Primary Blue: `#0969da` (links, CTAs, important elements)
- Hover Blue: `#0860ca`
- Active Blue: `#0757ba`

**Neutral Colors:**
- Text Primary: `#24292f` (main text)
- Text Secondary: `#57606a` (muted text, descriptions)
- Background: `#ffffff` (main background)
- Background Secondary: `#f6f8fa` (cards, hover states)
- Border: `#d0d7de` (borders, dividers)

**Status Colors:**
- Success: `#1a7f37`
- Error/Danger: `#cf222e`
- Warning: `#bf8700`

### Typography
- **Font Family**: `-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif`
- **Font Weights**: Use 300 (light), 400 (normal), 500 (medium), 600 (semibold)
- **Avoid**: Bold (700+) unless absolutely necessary

**Sizing Scale:**
- Page Title: `24px` - `32px` (weight: 300-400)
- Section Heading: `18px` - `20px` (weight: 400-500)
- Body Text: `14px` (weight: 400)
- Small Text: `12px` - `13px` (weight: 400)

### Layout & Spacing
- **Border Radius**: `6px` for buttons/inputs, `12px` for cards/modals
- **Spacing Scale**: `4px, 8px, 12px, 16px, 24px, 32px`
- **Max Width**: Content containers max `1200px`, forms/cards max `400-600px`
- **Whitespace**: Use generous whitespace - don't cram elements

### Components Style

**Buttons:**
```css
Primary: bg:#0969da, color:#fff, padding:12px 24px, radius:6px
Secondary: bg:#f6f8fa, color:#24292f, border:1px #d0d7de
Danger: bg:#cf222e, color:#fff
```

**Input Fields:**
```css
Border: 1px solid #d0d7de
Focus: border:#0969da, box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(9,105,218,0.1)
Padding: 12px, radius:6px
```

**Cards:**
```css
Background: #ffffff
Border: 1px solid #d0d7de
Border-radius: 6px
Box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(27,31,36,0.12) (on hover)
```

**Badges/Tags:**
```css
Background: #f6f8fa
Border: 1px solid #d0d7de
Padding: 6px 12px
Font-size: 13px
Border-radius: 6px
```

### Icons & Graphics
- **Use Icons Sparingly**: Only for critical actions (login, logout, profile, navigation)
- **Icon Library**: Inline SVG preferred, 16x16px or 20x20px
- **Style**: Outline style (stroke-based), not filled
- **Color**: Inherit from parent text color

### Interaction Patterns
**Hover Effects:**
- Subtle background color change (to `#f6f8fa`)
- No scale/transform effects
- Smooth transitions: `0.2s ease`

**Active States:**
- Slightly darker color
- No dramatic changes

**Disabled States:**
- Opacity: `0.5`
- Cursor: `not-allowed`

### Navigation & Layout Structure
**Navbar:**
- Fixed top, white background
- Height: `60px`
- Border-bottom: `1px solid #d0d7de`
- Logo left, user info right

**Sidebar:**
- Fixed left, white background
- Width: `240px`
- Border-right: `1px solid #d0d7de`
- Menu items: padding `8px 24px`, hover `#f6f8fa`

**Content Area:**
- Padding: `32px`
- Background: `#f6f8fa` (contrast with white cards)

### Forms & Data Entry
- Label above input
- Required fields: asterisk or `(required)` text
- Error messages: below input, color `#cf222e`, size `13px`
- Submit button: primary style, full width on mobile

### Feedback & Messaging
- Success: Light green background `#dafbe1`, green text `#1a7f37`
- Error: Light red background `#fff5f5`, red text `#cf222e`
- Warning: Light yellow background `#fff8c5`, yellow text `#bf8700`
- Info: Light blue background `#ddf4ff`, blue text `#0969da`

### Responsive Design
- Mobile-first approach
- Breakpoints: 768px (tablet), 1024px (desktop)
- Stack elements vertically on mobile
- Hide sidebar, use hamburger menu on mobile

### Accessibility
- Minimum contrast ratio: 4.5:1 for text
- Focus indicators visible and clear
- Semantic HTML elements
- ARIA labels where needed

### What to AVOID
❌ Dark themes
❌ Excessive animations/transitions
❌ Gradients (use solid colors)
❌ Drop shadows everywhere (use sparingly)
❌ Colorful/rainbow color schemes
❌ Emojis in UI (text content only)
❌ Multiple font families
❌ Comic Sans or decorative fonts
❌ Centered text for body content
❌ All caps text (except small labels)

